CalculatedFields.Name: Cost
CalculatedFields.Expression:
ifelse(
    ${CostType}="Amortized Cost", {amortized_cost},
    ${CostType}="Net Amortized Cost", {net_amortized_cost},
    ${CostType}="Billing Cost", {billing_cost},
    ${CostType}="Net Billing Cost", {billing_cost},
    {ondemand_cost}
)

CalculatedFields.Name: DateDim
CalculatedFields.Expression:
ifelse(
    ${DateGranularity}="Year", Year,
    ${DateGranularity}="Quarter", Quarter,
    ${DateGranularity}="Month", Month,
    ${DateGranularity}="Week", Week,
    ${DateGranularity}="Day", Day,
    ${DateGranularity}="Hour", Hour,
    ifelse(
        dateDiff(${StartDate},${EndDate},"DD")>730, Year,
        dateDiff(${StartDate},${EndDate},"DD")>365, Quarter,
        dateDiff(${StartDate},${EndDate},"DD")>180, Month,
        dateDiff(${StartDate},${EndDate},"DD")>60, Week,
        Day
    )
)

CalculatedFields.Name: DayInPeriod
CalculatedFields.Expression:
ifelse(
    InPeriodCurrent=1, dateDiff(${StartDate}, date), 
    InPeriod1=1, dateDiff(${Period1StartDate}, date),
    InPeriod2=1, dateDiff(${Period2StartDate}, date),
    -1 
)

CalculatedFields.Name: Period
CalculatedFields.Expression:
ifelse(
    InPeriodCurrent+InPeriod1+InPeriod2>=2, "OverlapPeriod",
    InPeriodCurrent=1, concat(toString(${DaysToCompare}), " days from ", formatDate(${StartDate}, "yyyy-MM-dd")),
    InPeriod1=1, concat(toString(${DaysToCompare}), " days from ", formatDate(${Period1StartDate}, "yyyy-MM-dd")),
    InPeriod2=1, concat(toString(${DaysToCompare}), " days from ", formatDate(${Period2StartDate}, "yyyy-MM-dd")),
    "NotInPeriod"
)

CalculatedFields.Name: charge_category
CalculatedFields.Expression:
ifelse(
    locate(service, 'Support')>0, '技术支持',
    locate(service, 'AWS Data Transfer')>0, '流量',
    right({charge_type}, 5)='Usage', '产品',
    '其他'
)
